#: ../../T/top-post.rst:5
msgid "top-post"
msgstr "top-post"

#: ../../T/top-post.rst:7
msgid "n\\., v\\."
msgstr "名詞・動詞"

#: ../../T/top-post.rst:9
msgid ""
"[common] To put the newly-added portion of an email or Usenet response "
"before the quoted part, as opposed to the more logical sequence of quoted "
"portion first with original following. The problem with this practice is "
"neatly summed up by the following FAQ entry:"
msgstr ""
"[一般的]引用された部分が先で元の文が続くというより論理的な順序とは逆に、メールやUsenetの返信の新たに加えた部分を引用部分の前に置くこと。この慣行の問題点は、次のFAQ項目にうまく要約されている。"

#: ../../T/top-post.rst:18
msgid ""
"This term is generally used pejoratively with the implication that the "
"offending person is a :ref:`newbie`\\, a Microsoft addict (Microsoft mail "
"tools produce a similar format by default), or simply a common-and-garden-"
"variety idiot."
msgstr ""
"この用語は一般に、違反者が\\ :ref:`newbie`\\ "
"、Microsoft中毒者(Microsoftのメールツールはデフォルトで似たような形式を生成する)、あるいは単にありふれた種類の馬鹿者であるという含みを持って、軽蔑的に使われる。"

#: ../../T/top-post.rst:20
msgid ""
"One major problem with top-posting is that people who do it all too "
"frequently quote the *entire* parent message rather than trimming it down to"
" those portions relevent to their reply — this makes threads bulky and "
"unnecessarily difficult to read and arouses the righteous ire of experienced"
" Internet residents (this style is called \"TOFU\" for \"text over, "
"fullquote under\", or sometimes \"jeopardy-style quoting\"). Another problem"
" is that top-posters often word their replies on the assumption that you "
"just read the previous message, even though their perversity has put it "
"further down the page than you have yet read. Oppose :ref:`bottom-post`\\."
msgstr ""
"top-postingの一つの大きな問題は、それをする人々があまりにも頻繁に、返信に関連する部分に削り込む代わりに親メッセージ\\ *全体*\\ "
"を引用することである——これはスレッドをかさばらせ、不必要に読みにくくし、経験豊富なインターネット住民の正当な怒りをかき立てる(この文体は\"text "
"over, fullquote under\"を表す\"TOFU\"、または時に\"jeopardy-style "
"quoting\"と呼ばれる)。もう一つの問題は、top-"
"posterがしばしば、自分のひねくれた行いによって前のメッセージがあなたがまだ読んだところより下に置かれているにもかかわらず、あなたが前のメッセージを読んだばかりだという前提で返信を書くことである。\\"
" :ref:`bottom-post`\\ と対比せよ。"
